body:
### Welcome to Joonha's Blog
This is a temporary website until I have the real thing up and running. 

### Latest Blog Post
#### Artisan
I want to be a speaker.
I want to be a fighter.
I want to be a negotiator.
I want to be a driver.
I want to be a cook.
I want to be a designer.
I want to be a programmer.
I want to be an entrepreneur.
I want to be a writer.
I want to be a poet.
I want to be a blogger.
I want to be a dancer.
I want to be a singer.
I want to be an actor.

I want to be all of these things and none of these things.

I am not a speaker.
I am not a fighter.
I am not a negotiator.
I am not a driver.
I am not a cook.
I am not a designer.
I am not a programmer.
I am not an entrepreneur.
I am not a writer.
I am not a poet.
I am not a blogger.
I am not a dancer.
I am not a singer.
I am not an actor.

I am me.
